features: Connect a headset or computer speakers to stream music in Stereo; connect a mono condenser Microphone for Skype chat, voice recognition, amateur radio, or DJ controller applications
Quick fix for a failed Audio port in a laptop. Work with USB hub or USB Extension cable; compatible with Chrome, Linux, Mac and Windows OS
C-Media HS-100B chipset. Supports Windows 7, 8, 10, Mac OSX and Linux
Compatible with USB 3.1, USB 2.0, and USB 1.0 Ports
3.5mm mic and speaker jacks. Sleek silver design. Plug-and-play, No driver required
description: Upgrade or fix your computer's sound in under a minute with this IOCrest USB Stereo sound adapter. No driver required, just plug it into any USB 3/2/1 port and your operating system will do the rest. The IOCrest SY-AUD20205 sleek aluminum shape makes it a great addition for high-end laptops and Ultra books. Perfect for connecting to USB hubs.
